renewed-contributions.title: The Methodological Character of Theoretical Concepts

additional-note: Volumes of this serial have distinctive titles.  Before concluding that a volume is in the public domain, search for renewals under its distinctive title. The active renewal for a contribution to the first volume was found under that volume's distinctive title, 'The Foundations of Science and the Concepts of Psychology and Psychoanalysis', and not under the serial title.
